url.name: Modelibra
url.description: Modelibra is a domain model framework. A domain model is a model of specific domain classes that describe the core data and their behavior. For prototypes and small applications, the model objects are saved in XML files.

url.name: Wicket
url.description: With proper mark-up/logic separation, a POJO data model, and a refreshing lack of XML, Apache Wicket makes developing web-apps simple and enjoyable again. Swap the boilerplate, complex debugging and brittle code for powerful, reusable components written with plain Java and HTML.
